column5: Well, as it goes, we have an opening for opening week at Wine Lake. $300 deposit already paid. We go in Friday morning since we are the first ones in. Tons of walleye, smallies and pike. Also trout will be shallow, hungry and big. Go to Wine Lake facebook or website to check it out. We can work out details. Just send me a private message if you are interested! Short notice but the trip of a life time! Hooks (HeHooksHimself)
Wow and I’m stuck with my niece’s graduation, but I can vouch that this is a good crew to fish with if anyone is interest.
Thanks Rich, I wish it was you! We have three, just need a 4th. It will be worth you while if you can do it! Hooks
